WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
That wasn't January of this year, that was January of 1961.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:11.000
That was Marvin Minsky in 1961 talking about reinforcement learning and pattern recognition.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:15.000
And everything that we are still working on today, over 60 years later.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:19.000
It's not to say that we haven't made some fascinating leaps and bounds.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:23.000
But when I tell people that I was working in reinforcement learning in the 90s,

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:26.000
a lot of them are surprised that we were doing that in the 90s.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:29.000
Well, we were doing it in the 50s and 60s.

